    Please note: due to bunkroom sizes, we are unable to accommodate specific cabin assignment requests with this
    option.
</p>
<p>
    "Premium Registration" - this covers the entire FurCoNZ, but with accommodation in the Waitawa Lodge. Each lodge has
    its own shared toilet and shower facilities as well as its own communal lounge and kitchenette, and the lodges
    include twin share private bedrooms. This option includes fully catered meals: supper for Thursday; breakfast, lunch
    and dinner for Friday and Saturday; breakfast and lunch for Sunday (8 main meals), and access to scheduled
    activities, panels, dances and lodge site area during the entire weekend.
</p>
<p>
    "Sponsor Registration" - this covers the entire FurcoNZ (as per above) + more! Including: goodie bag, first-in-line
    and extra goodies for meal services, housing in the premium Lake Lodges, plus more benefits, such as preferential
    treatment to events. (details to be finalized)
</p>
<p>
    "Super Sponsor Registration" -this is for a Sponsors (or Sponsors) who wish to go the extra mile for FurCoNZ. This
    covers the Sponsors perks (as per above) + more! Including: housing in the premium Lake Lodges with bedding and
    towels provided, customised con-badge, customised con T-shirt, plus even more benefits.
</p>
<p>
    "Day Pass" - this covers entry for Friday and/or Saturday from 9am until 9pm. You will have access to scheduled
    activities, panels, and common areas for the day(s) that you are visiting. Day Pass visitors can join us for Lunch
    and Dinner.
</p>

